  "original_title": "\u0b87\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0bb2 \u0baa\u0b95\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bb4\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bcd\u0baf\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Rain is likely in many areas today",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Department of Meteorology has predicted several times of rain in Upper, Sabaragamuwa and North-West provinces and Nuwara Eliya, Kandy, Galle and Matara districts.",
        "There is a chance of rain or thundershowers at some places in Uva province and Amparai and Batticaloa districts in the afternoon or night.",
        "Occasional gusty winds of up to 40 kilometers per hour may occur in the western slopes of the central hill country.",
        "There is a possibility of light rain over coastal areas from Puttalam through Colombo and Galle to Matara.",
        "Wind will blow from South-West direction with wind speed of 30-40 kmph. Wind speed may increase to 50-55 kmph over Puttalam through Mannar to Kangesanthurai and from Ambandottai to Pottuvil.",
        "From Puttalam to Kangesanthurai through Mannar and from Ambandottai to Pottuvil the sea surface will be turbulent from time to time. Other seas surrounding the country are expected to be moderate."
      ],
